00:31:03.300 --> 00:31:08.270
- Some-- on the one hand,
some non-believer will say,

00:31:08.270 --> 00:31:10.450
just calling.

00:31:10.450 --> 00:31:13.320
That's mentioning a
name, just calling.

00:31:13.320 --> 00:31:13.940
That's a call.

00:31:13.940 --> 00:31:17.537
Others will say, well,
the fact that I called--

00:31:17.537 --> 00:31:20.531
- [NON-ENGLISH SINGING]

00:32:58.460 --> 00:33:05.350
- Well, I don't go to church on
Sunday, don't get on my knees

00:33:05.350 --> 00:33:12.850
to pray, don't memorize
the books of the Bible.

00:33:12.850 --> 00:33:17.152
I got my own special way.

00:33:17.152 --> 00:33:27.400
Well, I know Jesus loves me
maybe just a little bit more.

00:33:27.400 --> 00:33:31.206
I've fallen on my
knees every Sunday

00:33:31.206 --> 00:33:35.250
at Ghirardelli's candy Store.

00:33:35.250 --> 00:33:37.420
