00:33:37.420 --> 00:33:39.700
- Another project, which
was quite interesting,

00:33:39.700 --> 00:33:44.150
because it happened just in
the moment of this Charlie

00:33:44.150 --> 00:33:50.220
Hebdo and all this interesting
historical moments,

00:33:50.220 --> 00:33:54.430
was "Toxic Psalms,"
where we research,

00:33:54.430 --> 00:33:59.720
again, this collective
operation, and especially

00:33:59.720 --> 00:34:05.650
what happens when collective
gets infected with ideology.

00:34:05.650 --> 00:34:09.940
So through the research
of Hannah Arendt,

00:34:09.940 --> 00:34:12.340
and her observations
in Jerusalem,

00:34:12.340 --> 00:34:16.330
and similar experiments,
such as Milgram experiment,

00:34:16.330 --> 00:34:21.820
and Lucifer effect, and all
kind of banality of evil,

00:34:21.820 --> 00:34:24.730
we brought a project
which was actually somehow

00:34:24.730 --> 00:34:29.080
a reflection of Palestine,
Syria, Pussy Riots,

00:34:29.080 --> 00:34:33.610
and all these situations around
the world where religion is

00:34:33.610 --> 00:34:37.510
becoming the main reason of
murderous violence in today's

00:34:37.510 --> 00:34:39.080
world.

00:34:39.080 --> 00:34:42.400
So it was kind of reflection
of human brutality,

00:34:42.400 --> 00:34:46.850
and man killing for the
glory of their Psalms.

00:34:46.850 --> 00:34:48.540
I never want to be agitator.

00:34:48.540 --> 00:34:49.880
We have to do something.

00:34:49.880 --> 00:34:51.010
I don't like this role.

00:34:51.010 --> 00:34:57.340
But again, the message was
that we probably should not

00:34:57.340 --> 00:35:00.580
be hiding behind a big Other.

00:35:00.580 --> 00:35:04.038
So that's "Toxic Psalms."

00:35:04.038 --> 00:35:07.020
