While this is running,
music was very

00:37:17.160 --> 00:37:22.620
diverse, from Rachmaninoff,
to contemporary music

00:37:22.620 --> 00:37:28.320
from Nordic countries,
to some early music,

00:37:28.320 --> 00:37:30.690
even medieval polyphony.

00:37:30.690 --> 00:37:35.070
So it was very, let's
say, eclectic musically.

