00:43:29.745 --> 00:43:37.500
OK, so I hope that you get a
little bit of impression what

00:43:37.500 --> 00:43:41.550
Choregie is, or
how deep love can

00:43:41.550 --> 00:43:44.490
be to the choirs,
and this big love,

00:43:44.490 --> 00:43:49.470
and can be also very
problematical love.

00:43:49.470 --> 00:43:51.360
Because it's always
a lot of people

00:43:51.360 --> 00:43:59.830
with different characters,
with different problems.

00:43:59.830 --> 00:44:02.550
So it's a very
special work to work

00:44:02.550 --> 00:44:05.370
with these big groups,
especially when you

00:44:05.370 --> 00:44:08.910
work on contemporary music,
which is not easy to study.

00:44:08.910 --> 00:44:12.000
And early music is also
difficult to memorize

00:44:12.000 --> 00:44:13.590
and to digest.

00:44:13.590 --> 00:44:18.330
But I think that when things
are studied and done, then

00:44:18.330 --> 00:44:22.450
it gives a really
special experience.

00:44:22.450 --> 00:44:26.370
And I really like doing it.

